description.narrative: Promotion of ECD was strengthened by the launch of ECD campaign “EarlyMomentsMatter” in partnership with ONPPE. It was an opportunity to bring together national experts and increase access to quality services. For infants and mothers, there was a revived engagement of health authorities on sectoral interventions such as immunization, neonatal and mother health. EMTCT evaluation was completed and the maternal death audit system implemented with the H6 group is being reinforced. The government adopted a new Executive Decree setting the conditions of ECD centers and will be followed by implementating actions to strengthen early learning and care in these centers. | Status:Constrained | As-of Date:29/12/2019
